snippet.textDisplay:
First of all, a very warm welcome to Shilpa Rao in Cokestudio! One who actually thought of introducing Cokestudio with an Indian singer like Shilpa Rao has to be appreciated! She has got that very specific voice for this type of song! WELL DONE SHILPA! love her MTV version of KAMLI. <3
secondly, the woman! i don't know what instrument that was, but she played it with intense care and depth! that whole minute was made totally because of her! and lastly shilpa looked stunning! BEST LINE OF THE SONG : 'yaar nu milay gi aj laash yaar di' !!
lastly, noori was no bad! applaud to everyone!
